<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm navbar-toggleable-sm navbar-light bg-white border-bottom box-shadow mb-3">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">AME</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target=".navbar-collapse" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent"
                        aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="navbar-collapse collapse d-sm-inline-flex justify-content-between">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav flex-grow-1">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark home-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark home-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="ContactUs">Contact Us</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link text-dark login-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Login">Login</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="~/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Welcome to Our AME School</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #9400D3, #000000, #ffffff); /* Gradient from violet to black to white */
            color: white; /* Set text color to white */
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .image-container {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }

            .image-container img {
                width: 80%;
                max-width: 400px;
                height: auto;
            }

        .content-container {
            flex: 1;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: white; /* Set title color to white */
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
            font-weight: bold; /* Make title bold */
            text-align: center; /* Center the title */
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: white; /* Set paragraph color to white */
            animation: slideIn 2s ease-in-out;
        }
     
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-container">
            <h1 id="title">Welcome to AME School</h1>
            <p>Our school is considered a major factor in establishing the people of the nation. Therefore, it aims to improve the student’s academic, cultural, and athletic level. Therefore, the school conducts summer training to improve the student’s academic, athletic, and cultural level.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <img src="~/image/Annotation 2024-03-18 121119.png" alt="School Image">
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="~/js/site.js"></script>
</body>

</html>

